dc_title_s: LiDAR-Derived Bare Earth Points for Clark County, WI 2018
dc_description_s: This data represents LiDAR-derived bare earth points for Clark County, Wisconsin in 2018. Bare earth LiDAR is digital elevation data of the terrain surface consisting of irregularly spaced points, each with x/y location coordinates and z-value. The data have been subjected to automated and manual editing to remove vegetation, buildings, and other man-made structures. This data is available in both LAS and TXT formats.
